                        <interp inst="t18770305-name-48" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN MACINTYRE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a warder of Coldbath Fields—I was present here when the prisoner was charged and sentenced to eighteen months' im<lb></lb>prisonment—I proved five previous convictions against him.</p>
               <p>
